cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG-U interface IP address to an unreachable subnet '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failures, preventing the CU from establishing NG-U connection to the UPF.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_dl timing parameters to [0, 0] (invalid values) will cause timing misalignment in front-haul processing, leading to synchronization failures and data transmission errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_dl 定時參數設定為 [0, 0]（無效值）會導致前傳處理中的定時錯位，造成同步失敗和數據傳輸錯誤。
